Promises and Observable
responsible for handling asynchronous requests.
Promise:
can handle single response from the same response
Not cancelable in nature.

Not lazy it can be exucuted immidate after the creation.
Observable:
can handle multiple response from the same response.
can cancelable in nature.
using unsubscribe()
Lazt in nature, dosent return anything untill you subscrive using subscribe method.
